# 🧮 Task 2 — Formula Thinking

## 1️⃣ Formula Field — Full Name

```text
First_Name + " " + Last_Name
```

### Why should this be automatic?

- Prevents typing mistakes
- Saves user time
- Keeps naming format consistent

---

## 2️⃣ Formula Field — Remaining Seats

```text
Total_Seats - Filled_Seats
```

### Why should this be automatic?

- Shows live seat availability
- Prevents overbooking
- Helps during admissions

---

## 3️⃣ Formula Field — Percentage

```text
(Obtained_Marks / Total_Marks) * 100
```

### Why should this be automatic?

- Gives accurate calculations
- Removes manual calculation errors
- Useful for ranking and reports

---

# ✅ Task 3 — Validation Rule Thinking

## 1️⃣ Email Cannot Be Blank

```text
ISBLANK(Email)
```

### What problem does this prevent?

- Prevents incomplete student records
- Ensures communication is possible

---

## 2️⃣ Student Age Cannot Be Negative

```text
Age__c < 0
```

### What problem does this prevent?

- Prevents invalid data entry
- Ensures realistic student records

---

## 3️⃣ Filled Seats Cannot Exceed Total Seats

```text
Filled_Seats__c > Total_Seats__c
```

### What problem does this prevent?

- Prevents over-admission
- Maintains correct seat allocation

